*** Settings ***

Documentation     Test case checks if valid signs are placed when making a move on a board

Library           SeleniumLibrary           run_on_failure=Nothing

*** Variables ***

${URL}            http://localhost:8000/
${BROWSER}        chrome
${CIRCLE}         fa-regular fa-circle
${CROSS}          fa fa-times

*** Test Cases ***

Test Tic Tac Toe
    Open Browser To Tic Tac Toe Game
    Place X    square-1
    Check X    square-1
    Check O    square-2

*** Keywords ***
Open Browser To Tic Tac Toe Game
    Open Browser    ${URL}    ${BROWSER}

Place X
    [Arguments]    ${square}
    Click Element   xpath=//div[@id="${square}"]

Check X
    [Arguments]    ${square}
    ${element}=    Get Element Attribute    xpath=//div[@id="${square}"]//span[@class="${CROSS}"]     element
    Run Keyword And Return Status    Element Should Be Visible    ${element}

Check O
    [Arguments]    ${square}
    ${element}=    Get Element Attribute    xpath=//div[@id="${square}"]//span[@class="${CIRCLE}"]     element
    Run Keyword And Return Status    Element Should Be Visible    ${element}
